                <note rend="inline" type="source">714.1515/591: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Guatemala</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Geissler</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Guatemala</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-03-22T13:00:00-06:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 22, 1928—1 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received 4:57 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>26. I have communicated the contents of the Department’s March 21, 7 p.m., to
                    President Chacon orally and to the Foreign Office by memorandum.</p>
                <p>The President says that the matter will be considered this afternoon at special
                    meeting of the Cabinet and that the decision will be communicated to me
                    immediately.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Geissler</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
